  "description": "Use this skill when building or customizing Lightning Web Components for B2B Commerce or D2C LWR storefronts \u2014 product display tiles, cart line-item components, checkout step components, wishlist buttons, and product comparison widgets that rely on Commerce Storefront wire adapters from the commerce namespace. NOT for standard LWC development outside a Commerce store context, not for Aura-based Community Builder components, and not for legacy B2B Commerce (CloudCraze) Aura widgets.",
  "file_location": "skills/lwc/commerce-lwc-components",
  "id": "lwc/commerce-lwc-components",
  "inputs": [
    "Store type: B2B Commerce or D2C (determines available wire adapters)",
    "Component role: product display, cart, checkout step, wishlist, or comparison",
